videos.description: Oregon's Francis Okoro attempts to put up the short-range shot, but UNC's Armando Bacot meets him at the top for the rejection off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bacot comes up with big-time rejection on Okoro) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bacot comes up with big-time rejection on Okoro

videos.description: Cole Anthony steals the inbound pass and races downcourt to slam home a one-handed dunk with authority to cap the break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony gets the steal and fast-break slam) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anthony gets the steal and fast-break slam
